+.TH ldapsetupfullname 1 "July 01, 2026"
+
+.SH NAME
+ldapsetupfullname \- update cn and gecos attribute of an LDAP user.
+
+.SH SYNOPSIS
+.B ldapsetupfullname
+.RB <username | uid>
+.RB <full name>
+
+.SH OPTIONS
+.TP
+.B [<username | uid> <full name>]
+  LDAP username and user's full name. If it contains spaces, enclose it in double quotes.
+
+.SH "SEE ALSO"
+ldapdeleteuser(1), ldapaddgroup(1), ldapaddusertogroup(1), ldapmodifyuser(1), ldapscripts(5).
+
